{
  "stem": "13874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would like to describe that situation by itself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For it will lead to my conclusions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have any job, regular jobs, which is hard labor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not put in hard labor because they just didn't have enough facilities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- everybody had to be out of the barracks in the morning after breakfast.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we either stood around freezing at the parade grounds, or we ran around to get warm-- of course in groups, not individually.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- we was-- we were exercised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Running around.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And quite a few collapsed from the rigor of the weather and the conditions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roll call was twice a day, in the morning at 5 o' clock, and in the evening at 6:00.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during one of the roll calls, towards the end of my stay, one prisoner had escaped.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the commandant said, you stay here and-- and stand here till that prisoner's been recaptured.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were standing there all night at attention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of us fell down and couldn't stay at attention.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Since there were several thousand people, those more or less in the middle had it a little easier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I must have dozed off, and I suddenly I was still on my feet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was hit in the back with a rifle butt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Luckily for me, I did not hit the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could catch myself and got up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or they would have killed me right then and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That morning, at 6 o'clock after sunrise, we were allowed one hour to go back and have breakfast.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The place was littered with people who had collapsed-- quite a few.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That is they were all dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was recaptured the next evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
